MEI Daemon-side
---------------
do all tiny funcs
do all big (calib) funcs

MEI Client-side
---------------
call all tiny funcs
call all big funcs
error checking
pretty printing



Error Handling:
--------------
client-side functions will return:
  DSP_OK (0) if everything was a-ok
  a DSP_ error, as given by the proxied MEI function, for wrappers
  a MEID_ERR_ error, if:  complex function barfs
                          Send/Receive fails
                          function not implemented

